remarks.code:
using ( var progress = SI.StartProgress( "building ..." ) ) {
  progress.Step( 1.0 );
  SI.Build();
}

using ( var progress = SI.StartProgress( "building ..." ) ) {
  progress.Step( 1.0 );
  SI.Rebuild();
}

example.code:
var poly = SI.NewInstance<Hisui.Spatial.IPolyline>();
var mesh = SI.NewInstance<Hisui.Spatial.IPolygonMesh>();
var tris = SI.NewInstance<Hisui.Spatial.ITriangleSoup>();

member.example:
The 2 lines below will get a same entry.

var entry1 = SI.FindEntry( new int[] { 3, 5, 2 } );
var entry2 = SI.Document.Entries[3].Entries[5].Entries[2];

The 2 lines below are equivalent.

var entry1 = SI.FindEntry( new int[] { 3, 5, 2 } );
var entry2 = SI.FindEntry( "3.5.2" );

